    • Constructor Detail

      • StandardLevel

        public StandardLevel(int scoreToComplete,
                     int steps,
                     int boardSize,
                     String walls)
        Constructs a StandardLevel instance with the constructor of the superclass Level and fills up the board with random Candy instances and the given walls.
        Parameters:
        scoreToComplete - the score required to complete the level
        steps - the maximum steps that can be used on this level
        boardSize - the dimensions of the board, a Level's board is always quadratic
        walls - the template String representing the coordinates of the walls
        See Also:
        LevelBuilder.processCoordinateString(java.lang.String)
